import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http'; import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'app-root', templateUrl: './app.component.html', styleUrls: ['./app.component.css'] }) export class AppComponent implements OnInit{ title = 'Dating AppTestotot'; users:any; constructor(private http: HttpClient){} ngOnInit(): void { this.http.get('https://localhost:5001/api/users').subscribe({ next:response=>this.users = response, error:error=>console.log(error), complete:()=> console.log('Request has completedng') }) } }
